<h2 id="lessons" class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2 mt-4">Lessons Learned</h2>
<ol class="list-decimal list-inside">
    <li>Don't Forget about audio!</li>
    <li>We followed a standard audio pipeline and it worked well for us.</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="learned" class="font-semibold mt-4">How We Learned This</h3>
<h4>Lesson 1</h4>
<p> From other projects, we know audio is often neglected until the later stages of production, which can lead to underdeveloped products and a lack of player feedback.
    We wanted to address audio early by finding and implementing placeholder sounds before finding final assets, which worked well for us.     
</p>

